# How to run the code

1. Install the required packages

```bash
pip install pandas numpy flask
```

2. Run the code

```bash
python app.py
```

3. Open the browser and go to http://127.0.0.1:5000/

4. Enter the number of processes and resources

5. Enter the allocation, request, and available resources

6. Click on the "Check Safety" button to check if the system is safe

7. The result will be displayed on the screen
